description: Pairwise comparison of the class1 catalytic domains from the DUF2 (DUF2) and exbB (exbB) families. The cross-family RMSD is the average RMSD between pairs of structures from different families, and is larger than the total RMSD, which compares structures both within- and between-families. TM scores are bound between 0 and 1. This alignment was generated automatically using 3DCOMB (Wang et al. 2011) and was not corrected with any manual adjustment.
